elements.content: Look for a vintage, statement sofa for your seating area. Scour Ebay, or go to garage sales in your town!
Also consider unusual or minimalistic stools. Overstock sites are a great place to find affordable versions.
Vintage chairs are also a great choice. They usually become a focal piece of the office, not just a comfy place to sit.
